    <title>Generalized metric tree arrangements and Dressians</title>
    <summary>  Metric trees and metric tree arrangements index cones in the polyhedral fan
structure in Dressian Dr(2, n) and Dr(3, n) respectively. We study the
adjacency of cones in Dressian Dr(3, n) and introduce general Whitehead moves
which provide a condition for adjacency of cones in Dr(3, n) in terms of the
associated metric tree arrangements. Based on these results we introduce the
notion of generalized metric tree arrangements which parameterize points in
Dr(k, n) and extend previously known results to Dr(k, n).
</summary>
